---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
import Heading from "../components/Heading.astro"
import CtaButton from "../components/CtaButton.astro"
import {
  GITHUB_ISSUES_URL,
  DISCORD_URL,
  DOCUMENTATION_URL,
  TWITTER_URL,
} from "../config"

const title = `Support DDEV`
---

<Layout title={title}>
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-24">
    <Heading title={title} subtitle={`We’d love your help!`} />
    <div class="prose text-lg my-12">
      <p>
        DDEV exists because of the generosity of community members and sponsors.<br
        />
        There are several ways to get involved and we’d love for you to join us.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose mt-12">
      <h2>File an Issue or PR</h2>

      <p>
        If you have an idea, or you found a bug, or you’re a devops whiz with a
        PR to contribute, please take the time to file a GitHub Issue or Pull
        Request.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 mb-12 flex w-2/5 -mx-2">
      <CtaButton
        text="Check Out GitHub Issues →"
        href={GITHUB_ISSUES_URL}
        type="hollow"
        target="_blank"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="prose mt-12">
      <h2>Improve the Docs</h2>
      <p>
        It doesn’t matter whether you’ve found a typo, can wordsmith something
        to better explain or fit our style guide, or you’d like to suggest an
        entirely new section or use case. We’d be happy to have your input!
      </p>

      <figure>
        <img
          src="/img/edit-docs.png"
          alt="Screenshot visually highlighting the “Edit this page” icon in the docs and pointing to its corresponding GitHub URL"
        />
        <figcaption>
          The pencil icon in the published docs links to the relevant GitHub
          source for suggestions.
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 mb-12 flex w-2/5 -mx-2">
      <CtaButton
        text="Visit the Docs →"
        href={DOCUMENTATION_URL}
        type="hollow"
        target="_blank"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="prose mt-12">
      <h2>Sponsor Development</h2>
      <p>
        We’re grateful for our sponsors, and all contributions to the DDEV
        Foundation go entirely toward development. We can always use resources
        to help attract contributors, cover test-running costs, and try to
        secure DDEV’s future.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 mb-12 flex w-2/5 -mx-2">
      <CtaButton
        text="Sponsor Randy on GitHub →"
        href="https://github.com/sponsors/rfay"
        type="hollow"
        target="_blank"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="prose mt-12">
      <h2>Help Others</h2>
      <p>
        There’s no shortage of questions on Discord, GitHub, and Stack Overflow.
        If you have the time to help someone out, it helps us out and lets us
        focus more on development.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 mb-12 flex w-2/5 -mx-2">
      <CtaButton
        text="Say Hi in Discord →"
        href={DISCORD_URL}
        type="hollow"
        target="_blank"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="prose mt-12">
      <h2>Spread the Word</h2>
      <p>
        If you like using DDEV, don’t keep it to yourself! Star the project on
        GitHub and make sure we know about your latest blog post, tweet, or
        YouTube video.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 mb-12 flex w-2/5 -mx-2">
      <CtaButton
        text="#DDEV on Twitter →"
        href={`https://twitter.com/hashtag/DDEV`}
        type="hollow"
        target="_blank"
      />
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
